Extension Name: SimpleCount
Author: SvennD

Extension Description: This replaces the default exact number of the forum with an approximate number; The idea is based on the counting system in Wolfram Alpha. The code was copy'd from TimeAgo ext by MuhClaren so any references are not coincident.

Extension Version: 0.0.2

Features:
Fully customization in ACP
Works on viewforum.php and index.php
Works in all styles
No JS

example :
